problem_text_cn: 如图,AB是⊙O的直径,点C,D,E均在⊙O上,若∠ACD=40°,则∠BED的度数为()
problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, AB is the diameter of ⊙O, points C, D, and E are all on ⊙O, if ∠ACD = N_0, then the degree of ∠BED is ()
raw_answer: 解:∵AB为⊙O的直径,∴⁀{ADB}的度数是180°,∵∠ACD=40°,∴⁀{AD}的度数是80°,∴⁀{BD}的度数是100°,∴∠BED=\frac{1}{2}×100°=50°,故选:A．
